snippet.title: Labyrinth of Zangetsu - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1922960/Labyrinth_of_Zangetsu/

Fight Japanese folklore inspired Yokai in a stunning ink-brush illustrated Dungeon Crawler! Set in the moonlit city of Ido, the world has blackened under the 'Ink of Ruin' disaster. Conscript a team of warriors to venture deep into the Labyrinths to conquer and sanctify the land!

Follow PQube Games on social media!
Discord: https://discord.gg/pqubegames 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pqubegames/
